Hellplague:
 
"Sure, i'll help," the femme said as she walked around to the other side where the panel was located.

rm2kmidi <kraftlos@...> wrote:
Celeron examined the damage near Hellplague's room, then returned to
check on the new panel, it was not yet cool.

"Would you like to help me remove the damaged panels near you room. 
Then I will be able to determine if there is any structural damage,
and we might be able to make a replacement pannel."


"HA!  Is that all you got?  You boasted such power, such skill!  Where is your power and skill now?  You disappoint me, ha ha ha haa!"
